"48%。([#257](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim/pull/257)) "
"(@williamleong)"

#: ../../../changelog.md:45
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Use STRtree intersects predicate for lidar map segment filtering, ~26% "
