"/ir-sim/pull/255)) (@williamleong)"
msgstr ""
"使用 STRtree intersects 谓词进行 lidar 地图线段过滤，PNG 地图场景中 lidar 步进加快约 "
"26%。([#255](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim/pull/255)) "
"(@williamleong)"

#: ../../../changelog.md:46
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Cache geometry validity and streamline lidar map ray intersection, ~18% "
