"/ir-sim/pull/254)) (@williamleong)"
msgstr ""
"缓存几何有效性并简化 lidar 地图射线求交，PNG 地图场景中 lidar 步进加快约 "
"18%。([#254](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim/pull/254)) "
"(@williamleong)"

