msgstr ""
"为无效的 YAML 配置键新增拼写错误检测与建议。([#227](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-"
"sim/pull/227))"

#: ../../../changelog.md:63
msgid ""
"Centralize kinematics metadata (default color, state_dim, description) in"
