"([#237](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim/pull/237))"
msgstr ""
"将运动学元数据（默认颜色、state_dim、描述）集中到 handler "
"注册表，使运动学更易于添加。([#237](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim/pull/237))"

#: ../../../changelog.md:66
