"([#230](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim/pull/230)) (@williamleong)"
msgstr ""
"通过逐帧读取和保存而非将所有图像载入内存，提升保存动画的健壮性。([#230](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-"
"sim/pull/230)) (@williamleong)"

#: ../../../changelog.md:69
msgid ""
"Add \"Dynamic Object Management\" section to the Make Environment "
"documentation. ([#251](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim/pull/251))"
msgstr ""
"在 Make Environment 文档中新增“动态物体管理”章节。([#251](https://github.com/hanruihua"
"/ir-sim/pull/251))"

