#: ../../../changelog.md:72
msgid "2.9.1 (2026-02-16)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../changelog.md:75
msgid ""
"Add Perlin noise and image-based grid map generators, new JPS (Jump Point"
" Search) and Informed RRT* path planners, and refactor existing planners "
"(A*, RRT, RRT*, PRM) to use the `EnvGridMap` protocol. #215 "
"(@KevinLADLee)"
msgstr ""
"新增 Perlin 噪声和基于图像的栅格地图生成器、新的 JPS（跳点搜索）和 Informed RRT* "
"路径规划器，并重构现有规划器（A*、RRT、RRT*、PRM）以使用 `EnvGridMap` 协议。#215 (@KevinLADLee)"

#: ../../../changelog.md:76
msgid ""
"Drop Python 3.9 support, add Python 3.14 support. Raise minimum Python "
"version to 3.10, modernize type annotations (`Optional`/`Union` to `X | "
"Y` syntax). #216"
msgstr ""
"移除 Python 3.9 支持，新增 Python 3.14 支持。将最低 Python 版本提升至 "
"3.10，现代化类型注解（`Optional`/`Union` 改为 `X | Y` 语法）。#216"

#: ../../../changelog.md:77
msgid ""
"Add optional `reload` parameter to `set_random_seed()` that regenerates "
"random obstacles with the new seed when set to `True`. #210"
msgstr "为 `set_random_seed()` 新增可选 `reload` 参数，设为 `True` 时用新种子重新生成随机障碍物。#210"

#: ../../../changelog.md:78
msgid ""
"Default animation filename to the world name when not explicitly "
"specified. #221"
msgstr "未显式指定时，动画文件名默认使用世界名称。#221"

#: ../../../changelog.md:81
msgid ""
"Add grid-based collision detection for obstacle maps using grid array "
"lookup for faster detection, cache STRtree in `ObstacleMap`. #205"
msgstr "为障碍物地图新增基于栅格的碰撞检测，使用栅格数组查找以加速检测，并在 `ObstacleMap` 中缓存 STRtree。#205"

#: ../../../changelog.md:84
msgid ""
"Add input validation decorators (`validate_shape`, `validate_length`, "
"`ensure_column_vector`, `ensure_numpy`) for kinematics and utility "
"functions. #209"
msgstr "为运动学和工具函数新增输入校验装饰器（`validate_shape`、`validate_length`、`ensure_column_vector`、`ensure_numpy`）。#209"

#: ../../../changelog.md:87
msgid "Refine README. #222"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../changelog.md:88
msgid "Add grid map configuration and path planning documentation. #215"
msgstr "新增栅格地图配置和路径规划文档。#215"

#: ../../../changelog.md:90
msgid "2.9.0 (2026-01-26)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../changelog.md:92
msgid ""
"This version adds multi-environment support with instance-based "
"parameters, allowing multiple independent simulation environments to run "
"simultaneously. It also introduces 1D ToF sensor support and keyboard "
"improvements."
msgstr "此版本新增了基于实例参数的多环境支持，允许多个独立的仿真环境同时运行。还引入了 1D ToF 传感器支持和键盘改进。"

#: ../../../changelog.md:95
msgid ""
"Add 1D ToF (Time-of-Flight) sensor support by setting lidar2d sensor "
"`number: 1` and `angle_range: 0`. ([#200](https://github.com/hanruihua"
"/ir-sim/pull/200))"
msgstr ""
"通过设置 lidar2d 传感器 `number: 1` 和 `angle_range: 0` 新增 1D "
"ToF（飞行时间）传感器支持。([#200](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim/pull/200))"

#: ../../../changelog.md:96
msgid ""
"Add multi-environment keyboard switching support. Only one environment "
"responds to keyboard input at a time; switching occurs via mouse click or"
" focus events. ([#192](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim/pull/192))"
msgstr ""
"新增多环境键盘切换支持。同一时刻仅一个环境响应键盘输入；通过鼠标点击或焦点事件切换。([#192](https://github.com/hanruihua"
"/ir-sim/pull/192))"

#: ../../../changelog.md:97
msgid ""
"Add `y` key to toggle display render window on/off. "
"([#194](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim/pull/194))"
msgstr "新增 `y` 键用于开关显示渲染窗口。([#194](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim/pull/194))"

#: ../../../changelog.md:100
msgid ""
"Environment parameters (`env_param`, `world_param`, `path_param`) are now"
" instance-based rather than global, enabling proper multi-environment "
"support. ([#191](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim/pull/191))"
msgstr ""
"环境参数（`env_param`、`world_param`、`path_param`）现为基于实例而非全局，从而支持正确的多环境运行。([#191](https://github.com/hanruihua"
"/ir-sim/pull/191))"

#: ../../../changelog.md:103
msgid ""
"Fix `robot` property to raise `IndexError` with clear message when no "
"robots exist. ([#188](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim/pull/188))"
msgstr ""
"修复 `robot` 属性，在不存在机器人时抛出带清晰信息的 "
"`IndexError`。([#188](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim/pull/188))"

#: ../../../changelog.md:104
msgid ""
"Fix `save_figure` to handle filenames with multiple dots correctly. "
"([#188](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-sim/pull/188))"
msgstr ""
"修复 `save_figure` 以正确处理含多个点的文件名。([#188](https://github.com/hanruihua/ir-"
"sim/pull/188))"

